The Imitation Game: During World War II, the English mathematical genius Alan Turing tries to crack the German Enigma code with help from fellow mathematicians.
TRON: A computer hacker is abducted into the digital world and forced to participate in gladiatorial games where his only chance of escape is with the help of a heroic security program.
WarGames: A young man finds a back door into a military central computer in which reality is confused with game-playing, possibly starting World War III.
